text: Bikkuzha () is a rural locality (a village) in Tazlarovsky Selsoviet, Zianchurinsky District, Bashkortostan, Russia. The population was 85 as of 2010. There is 1 street. == Geography == It is located 20 km from Isyangulovo, 10 km from Tazlarovo. == References == Category:Rural localities in Zianchurinsky District
title: Bikkuzha
